---
By: Dalai Lama
Source:
  URL: https://twitter.com/DalaiLama/status/990885997998096386
  Locus:
    Date: 30 Apr 2018
---
There is a link between our physical and verbal actions and emotions. If,
instead of anger, hatred and suspicion, we are moved by loving-kindness,
we will naturally have greater respect for others and our actions will
be non-violent.
